@312    = ~Stormbreaker~
@313    = ~Stormbreaker: +1 Warhammer

Stormbreaker is a blessed warhammer with a well known history amongst the bards of Icewind Dale. The great dwarven battlecleric, Hratan Bonecracker, wielded Stormbreaker in his many battles against various Aurilite and Talosian factions throughout the Dale.  His enemies fell by the dozens when he fought with his trusty hammer in hand, both to protect him and to bring justice to the wicked.

However, Hratan's days came to an end not on the field of battle, but at an inn.  As he had done so often, Hratan savored his final victory in many tankards of his favorite ale.  But on this night, Hratan was so drunk, in spite of his stupendous dwarven endurance, that he didn't realize that his life was melting away due to a terrible poison slipped into his last tankard.  

On the next morn, when the innkeeper came to rouse Hratan, he found the mighty cleric dead, Stormbreaker gone, and a note left on the nightstand.

"The cries for vengeance have been answered.  The slayer of so many of my brethren has finally paid the price for their murders.  Stormbreaker's days of slaying brothers and sisters of the Storm are at an end.

By Sweet Auril's Grace...  Stormsister Lysan"

And while the Aurilite Lysan was finally found and slain outside of the Vale of Shadows during Belhifet's Riegn of Terror years ago, the mighty warhammer Stormbreaker has never been recovered.

