@946    = ~The Golden Helm~
@947    = ~This magnificent (and rather ostentatious) golden helm has seen many days and many battles on the heads of many a noble champion and many who were less so.  But as is the case with most warriors, they do not die of old age, but in battle.  And this helm has bought and sold many times after such battles.

